{"tid":1747670,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港鐵為方便市民投票　明晚各路綫服務將維持至11時","createTime":"2019-11-23T10:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T01:55:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a10dac4369d8f8a2ef590c1fdd217375f3cb51d0","tid":1747670,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:24:21.000Z","msg":"港鐵表示，為支持區議會選舉，方便市民出外投票，除機場快綫外，港鐵會於車站加派人手，各鐵路綫，輕鐵及港鐵巴士的服務明天將維持至晚上11時。但紅磡站及大學站則未能在明天開放使用，個別車站出入口亦因受損情況嚴重，需要繼續關閉。<br />\n<br />\n至於其他車站，港鐵指會在安全情況下盡力維持車站開放。但假如風險增加或再有鐵路設施被嚴重破壞，為顧及乘客、港鐵員工及鐵路營運的安全，可能會調整甚至立即停止個別路段的列車服務，車站或其部份出入口也可能在短時間內或未能作事先通知的情況下關閉。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示會密切留意明天的情況，繼續評估風險狀況，請乘客出行前留意最新的服務安排。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1494014-20191123.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1494014-20191123.htm&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpKpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=be506ba8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1494014-20191123.htm&h=cd2cff2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1494014-20191123.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d53468d90ccc67a605ef2bc6b195588f716fa51e","tid":1747670,"uid":104044,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:25:40.000Z","msg":"票站唔係係你住既附近咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁做係方便咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32300b991e51ec07a9b76bfccc7d3f2a6f1b806","tid":1747670,"uid":53214,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:28:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47566ed2628993cf62bca3ae179f28a81500cc37","tid":1747670,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d53468d90ccc67a605ef2bc6b195588f716fa51e","tid":1747670,"uid":104044,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"